author: Master_Wu
title: Four tentacles!
review:
Whether your a fan of Mixels or not, I would recommend this set for any fan of Legos!

There are plenty of opportunities to play with this set, as well as use the parts to build your own Mixels!

There are a lot of joints in this set which is why I enjoyed building, playing and creating with this toy! I reccommend it for anyone!
